data.title: Stratovarius: Under Flaming Winter Skies
data.meta_description: Stratovarius: Under Flaming Winter Skies - Live in Tampere: Directed by Ville Lipiäinen. With Timo Kotipelto, Matias Kupiainen, Lauri Porra, Jens Johansson. 'Live In Tampere' marks the end of an era as well as a new beginning. This is one of the very last shows with drummer and key-member Jörg Michael.
